PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FThe Supermarine Spitfire could go back
OL,7,Finto production 90 years after its
OL,8,Ffirst flight ` if the dreams of a team
OL,9,Fof enthusiasts are realised.
OL,11,FThe next generation of the aircraft, a
OL,12,Fconcept model called the Aerolite
OL,13,FSpitfire Type 433, has been built by a
OL,14,Fteam of designers and engineers at a
OL,15,Ffraction of the cost of buying an
OL,16,Foriginal.
OL,18,FThe new two-seater model has been
OL,19,Fconstructed for about #750,000,
OL,20,Fcompared with the more than #3 million
OL,21,Fprice tag of an original Spitfire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
