OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FThe team revisited wartime government
OL,7,Fplans to replace diminishing supplies
OL,8,Fof aluminium for Spitfire fuselages
OL,9,Fwith a composite alternative called
OL,10,FGordon Aerolite.
OL,12,FThose plans were later abandoned in
OL,13,F1940, but this team have continued
OL,14,Fwith the designs to create the
OL,15,FAerolite Spitfire.
OL,17,FThey have used modern composites to
OL,18,Fbuild what could be the world's
OL,19,Fbiggest kit form aircraft.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FThe aircraft will supplement the ranks
OL,7,Fof the very rare original two-seater
OL,8,FSpitfire, originally built in
OL,9,FSouthampton, as there are only about a
OL,10,Fdozen remaining operational.
OL,12,FIts composite construction means there
OL,13,Fis no requirement for hangar storage
OL,14,Fas it is weather resistant.
OL,16,FThe full-scale concept model, which
OL,17,Fhas been unveiled in Bodmin, Cornwall,
OL,18,Fwill tour the UK this spring and
OL,19,Fsummer at up to 10 air shows and
OL,20,Fmilitary and classic motor festivals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FJeremy Meeson, chief executive of the
OL,7,Fmanufacturer Great British Supermarine
OL,8,FLtd, said: "The moment is right to
OL,9,Freimagine the Supermarine Spitfire
OL,10,Fbecause today's materials, propulsion,
OL,11,Fand digital engineering finally let us
OL,12,Fevolve an icon without losing what
OL,13,Fmade it exceptional.
OL,15,F"This design stays true to its 1940s'
OL,16,Flineage ` lightweight performance,
OL,17,Fbalance, and pilot connection ` while
OL,18,Fintroducing advanced composites,
OL,19,Fmodern power systems, and intelligent
OL,20,Favionics.
OL,26,@pD@LOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,F"Just as the original Spitfire pushed
OL,7,Fthe limits of its time, this one does
OL,8,Fthe same.
OL,10,F"A recreational aircraft designed for
OL,11,Fpilots and enthusiasts who demand
OL,12,Fauthenticity with real capability, it
OL,13,Fdelivers a flying experience rooted in
OL,14,Fheritage but engineered for now.
OL,16,F"We are considering investors for this
OL,17,Fambitious once-in-a-generation project.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,F"We know the appetite for Spitfire
OL,7,Fownership is huge and that for most
OL,8,Fpeople the price tag for an original
OL,9,Fis insurmountable.
OL,11,F"Our Spitfire, at a fraction of the
OL,12,Fcost, is an attractive proposition for
OL,13,Fprivate aircraft-owning consortia.
OL,15,F"Aerolite anticipates a brisk progress
OL,16,Ftowards full production with
OL,17,Fsignificant interest from UK and
OL,18,Finternational buyers and investors."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FDavid Spencer Evans, a former chairman
OL,7,Fof the Spitfire Society and the
OL,8,FSpitfire Heritage Trust, worked with
OL,9,FMr Meeson on delivering the project.
OL,11,F"We are continuing the Spitfire story
OL,12,Fin composite with this aeroplane," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We have a vicarious connection with
OL,16,Fthat original Spitfire, and we regard
OL,17,Four Spitfire as a continuation of the
OL,18,FSpitfire line.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@bO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,F"Every red-blooded Brit has some
OL,7,Faffection for the Spitfire. It's
OL,8,Fsomething beautiful.
OL,10,F"Everybody recognises the Spitfire.
OL,11,FIt's a wonderful machine.
OL,13,F"Nobody will let me fly a real
OL,14,FSpitfire, so I have to build my own,
OL,15,Fdon't I?
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,F"We are looking at a number of air
OL,7,Fshows this year to gauge the interest
OL,8,Fand also to invite potential investors
OL,9,Fto the project because it's going to
OL,10,Fbe an expensive business getting the
OL,11,Fprototype flying.
OL,13,F"We hope to do that in two and a half
OL,14,Fyears from a standing start.
OL,16,F"It's purely a fun aeroplane and it's
OL,17,Fthe sort of thing that a group of
OL,18,Ffriends in a flying club might pool
OL,19,Ftogether to buy the kit, put together
OL,20,Fand fly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
