PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779098804
OL,3,CSpitfire could return to production 90
OL,4,Cyears after first flight
OL,6,FThe Supermarine Spitfire became one of
OL,7,Fthe defining symbols of Britain during
OL,8,Fthe Second World War, playing a
OL,9,Fcrucial role in the Battle of Britain
OL,10,Fand helping secure Allied air
OL,11,Fsuperiority.
OL,13,FRenowned for its speed, agility and
OL,14,Fdistinctive elliptical wings, it
OL,15,Fremains one of the most well-known
OL,16,Faircraft ever built.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
